{"id":654223392,"lang":"cpp","time":"3 months, 2 weeks","timestamp":1646537242,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"17 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/654223392/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Rectangle Area","memory":"5.9 MB","code":"class Solution {\npublic:\n    int computeArea(int ax1, int ay1, int ax2, int ay2, int bx1, int by1, int bx2, int by2) {\n        int area1 = (ax2-ax1) * (ay2-ay1);\n        int area2 = (bx2-bx1) * (by2-by1);\n        int comarea = 0;\n        \n        int left = max(ax1, bx1);\n        int right = min(ax2, bx2);\n        int top = min(ay2, by2);\n        int bottom = max(ay1, by1);\n        \n        if(left < right && top > bottom)\n            comarea = (right-left) *(top-bottom);\n            \n        return area1 + area2 - comarea;\n    }\n};","compare_result":"","title_slug":"rectangle-area"}
